REM Title: Kali_Emerged
REM Description: Installs wsl Kali on windows host 
REM Author: evodefense
REM Target: Windows 10/11
REM This payload is usable to help windows users create a dragon
REM This is for use in good karma only with permission and within all applicable authoritys and regulations per your application.
REM I could not of made this without the community and amazing amount of educational material online for free. Thx

REM Enable the Windows Subsystem for Linux feature
DELAY 1000
GUI r
DELAY 500
STRING powershell
DELAY 500
ENTER
DELAY 500
STRING Enable-WindowsOptionalFeature -Online -FeatureName Microsoft-Windows-Subsystem-Linux
DELAY 500
ENTER

REM Restart the computer to complete the WSL 2 installation
DELAY 5000
STRING shutdown /r /t 0
DELAY 500
ENTER

REM Wait for the computer to restart
DELAY 60000

REM Install Kali Linux from the Microsoft Store
DELAY 1000
GUI r
DELAY 500
STRING Microsoft Store
DELAY 500
ENTER
DELAY 1000
STRING Kali Linux
DELAY 500
ENTER
DELAY 1000
STRING Install
DELAY 500
ENTER

REM Wait for the installation to complete
DELAY 80000

REM Launch Kali Linux
DELAY 1000
GUI r
DELAY 500
STRING Kali Linux
DELAY 500
ENTER
